Patch notes for all mods, including unreleased (I'm tired of maintaining separate ones): https://docs.google.com/document/d/1Fylr2cnjV92d5j7U7qTki2S7RAUvpkMsxgsz9Ayoy1E/edit?usp=sharing
    </description>
	<modIconPath IgnoreIfNoMatchingField="True">UI/HautsLogo_Draft0</modIconPath>
